  "body": "<p>You know those crazy, fun ideas that you get in your head in the middle of the night or while standing in the shower? I have quite a few of those that actually come to fruition, and this was definitely one of them. I've been dreaming up these shoefies for quite some time. Executing them in a place other than my driveway was something I thought would be really fun to do. At the end of June, I painted this in the Tieks parking lot. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5cf2122f8cec921e.jpg?v=1782539046\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>In the photo I posted on the 4th of July, I am wearing Tieks in Cardinal Red. They posted this one on their Instagram the same day: </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/68e8f7cd804be3f3.png?v=1782539048\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bbf05d0a9e762b46.png?v=1782539051\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>It was a really fun project and I also filmed <a href=\"https://youtu.be/rVq7PrFx71A\">a behind the scenes video</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7c749f18c682d68e.png?v=1782539055\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The photo with the kangaroo and the mustard yellow Tieks is mine! So neat.</p><p><strong>GIVEAWAY: One $100 Tieks E-Gift card - CLOSED</strong></p><p><strong>GIVEAWAY IS NOW CLOSED, THANKS TO ALL WHO ENTERED. LOVED READING YOUR FANTASTIC IDEAS OF WHAT TO PAINT ON THE GROUND! To enter </strong>to win a $100 e-gift card from Tieks, simply <strong>leave a comment on what you'd want painted on the ground - or what your favorite color is!</strong> Winner will be chosen at random and announced on this post Monday, September 12 after 9am Pacific. Good luck! <strong>WINNER IS: Kym! Congrats! You are the winner of the $100 gift card! Please send us an email hello(at)amytangerine(dot)com and we will get your info to Tieks!</strong></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}